Class:
Shape

Variables:
enum(Z, S, L, I, O, J, T) _type	# stores the type of shape
int[4][4] _shape				# the actual orientation of the current shape (0 or 2, be consistent with Matrix)
int _position_x					# x coordinate of the center, 0-9
int _position_y					# y coordinate of the center, 0-14


Methods:
##### constructor #####
Shape()							# default constructor, type will be randomly selected on object constructing
##### type related #####
char getType()					# return the char represent its type
void selectType()					# randomly set a type
##### position related #####
int getX()						# return the value fo _position_x
int getY()						# return the value fo _position_y
void moveDown()					
void moveRight()
void moveLeft()
void moveTo(int newX, int newY)	# set position with new values
##### rotation related #####
void rotateCW()						# rotate the shape clockwise
void rotateCC()						# rotate the shape conter-clockwise
##### shape related #####
int[4][4] getShape()				# return the actual 4x4 shape matrix
